snippet.title: GRINDSTONE - A Puzzle-Battle Splatter-Fest!
snippet.description:
Grindstone is a new puzzle-battling color-pathing creep-smushing game from CAPY, the studio who brought you Superbrothers: Sword & Sworcery EP, Might & Magic Clash of Heroes & Critter crunch.

Out now on Apple Arcade!

https://apple.co/-Grindstone


For more information on Grindstone, visit: 
https://www.grindstonegame.com/
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/grindstone-switch/

Follow Capy on Twitter, Facebook and Instagram:
https://twitter.com/CAPYGAMES
https://www.facebook.com/CAPYGAMES/
https://www.instagram.com/capygames/

Sign-up for our newsletter:
http://ow.ly/G4WD50CqHU0
